trans-unit.source: Represents a control that raises its <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click"></xref> event repeatedly from the time it is pressed until it is released.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en kontroll som opphøyer den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click"> </xref> hendelsen gjentatte ganger etter trykkes til den frigis.

trans-unit.source: A RepeatButton is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, which means that it can contain a single object of any type (such as a string, an image, or a panel).
trans-unit.target: En RepeatButton er en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, noe som betyr at det kan inneholde ett enkelt objekt av en annen type (for eksempel en streng, et bilde eller en panelet).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>

trans-unit.source: The RepeatButton class represents a control that is similar to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen RepeatButton representerer en kontroll som ligner på en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: However, repeat buttons give you control over when and how the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid Gjenta knapper gir deg kontroll over når og hvordan <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click>inntreffer.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click>

trans-unit.source: The RepeatButton raises the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click> event repeatedly from the time it is pressed until it is released.
trans-unit.target: RepeatButton opphøyer i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click>hendelsen gjentatte ganger etter trykkes til den frigis.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.ButtonBase.Click>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Delay%2A> property determines when the event begins.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Delay%2A>egenskapen bestemmer når hendelsen starter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Delay%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also control the interval of the repetitions with the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Interval%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også kontrollere tidsintervallet repetisjoner med den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Interval%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RepeatButton.Interval%2A>

trans-unit.source: Customizing the RepeatButton Control To apply the same property settings to multiple RepeatButton controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilpasse den RepeatButton kontrollen til gjelder samme egenskapsinnstillingene flere RepeatButton kontroller, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>Gi kontrollen unikt utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the RepeatButton, see [RepeatButton Syles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se delene og statusene som er spesifikke for RepeatButton, kan du se [RepeatButton Syles og maler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Dependency properties for this control might be set by the control’s default style.
trans-unit.target: Avhengighet egenskapene for denne kontrollen, kan angis ved kontrollens standardstilen.

trans-unit.source: If a property is set by a default style, the property might change from its default value when the control appears in the application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egenskap er satt av en standardstilen, kan endre egenskapen standardverdi når kontrollen vises i applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
trans-unit.target: Standardstilen er avhengig av hvilken stasjonær tema brukes når programmet kjører.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Default WPF Themes](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [standard WPF oppsett](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Setting a visual property will only have an effect if that property is both present in Button control's default template and is set by using a .
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Angi en visual egenskap trenger bare en effekt hvis egenskapen er begge finnes i standardmal for knappekontrollen og angis ved hjelp av en.

trans-unit.source: You can find a list of visual properties in the "Changing the Visual Structure of a Control" section in [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](../Topic/Customizing%20the%20Appearance%20of%20an%20Existing%20Control%20by%20Creating%20a%20ControlTemplate.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner en liste over visual egenskaper i delen "Endring i Visual strukturen av et kontroll" [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](../Topic/Customizing%20the%20Appearance%20of%20an%20Existing%20Control%20by%20Creating%20a%20ControlTemplate.md).
